Package frogger.model.actor.staticActor

Class StaticActor

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.image.ImageView
        • frogger.model.actor.Actor
          • frogger.model.actor.staticActor.StaticActor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Chomper, Digit, End
    public abstract class StaticActor
extends Actor

    StaticActor

    The StaticActor class is an abstract class contains the shared constructor which set the position of StaticActor instance

    Note: : StaticActor classes are not allowed to be instantiated thus it's need to be extended

    Since:
    1.0
